findings.title: Owner can disable trading / Contract is pausable
findings.description: The contract owner has the capability to pause or disable trading, which could potentially lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can mint new tokens
findings.description: The owner of the contract has the ability to mint new tokens, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can set buy/sell fees with an indefinite amount
findings.description: The contract owner has the ability to set buy and sell fees without any limitations, which could lead to unintended consequences.

findings.title: Owner can set max transaction limit
findings.description: The contract owner has the ability to set a maximum transaction limit, which could potentially lead to unintended consequences or restrictions on users.
